    title: "4.9/5 Average Rating",
    description: "Based on 50,000+ verified student reviews across all platforms. Our curated courses consistently deliver exceptional learning outcomes."
  },
  {
    icon: `<path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/>`,
    title: "Daily Fresh Deals",
    description: "Fresh Udemy coupons added every single day. Our team scours the web so you never miss a limited-time free course offer."
  },
  {
    icon: `<path d="M17 3H5c-1.11 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V7l-4-4zm-5 16c-1.66 0-3-1.34-3-3s1.34-3 3-3 3 1.34 3 3-1.34 3-3 3zm3-10H5V7h10v2z"/>`,
    title: "Lifetime Access",
    description: "Keep courses forever — once enrolled, your access never expires. Includes completion certificates, downloadable resources, and all future updates."
  },
  {
    icon: `<path d="M18 8h-1V6c0-2.76-2.24-5-5-5S7 3.24 7 6v2H6c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v10c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V10c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM9 6c0-1.66 1.34-3 3-3s3 1.34 3 3v2H9V6zm3 9c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2s.9-2 2-2 2 .9 2 2-.9 2-2 2z"/>`,
    title: "No Hidden Fees",
    description: "100% free — no credit card required, no subscription, no catch. We partner with instructors who want to reach more students worldwide."
  },
  {
