    a: "Udemy coupon validity typically ranges from 1–7 days, though some last up to a month. Each coupon also has a maximum enrollment limit (usually 1,000 students). We recommend enrolling immediately when you find a course you want — free spots fill up fast!"
  },
  {
    icon: "M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z",
    q: "Will I receive a certificate after completing a free course?",
    a: "Absolutely! Courses enrolled via our 100% off coupons include the exact same benefits as paid courses — including an official Udemy completion certificate, lifetime access, downloadable resources, and instructor Q&A support."
